EgeOfTheWorld.out is compilation made with the linux system

the codes are in "common.h" and "main.cpp"

The Data of The Player are automatically saved in playerstatus.txt.

When you want to terminate the game, just close the window or ctrl+c to end it.

Next time when you want to read the record, input the file name playerstatus.txt

If you want to keep the record, manually change its name after each game, or it will be overwritten next time.
